  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_131",
    "english": "Demon. Although an inhabitant of the Demon Realm, they can be found in the human world, in places where demonic organizations lie, such as Tokyo Kingdom or Yomihara. They are weak among demons, so rather than moving alone, they join organizations, and use their superhuman strength in the human world to become thugs and threaten others.",
